{"tid":1561330,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果大家真係當呢首係國歌，唔該俾少少尊重","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:31:29.000Z","uid":273176,"like":323,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"e87645792179beb8b249e32fa257dcc2cba1b046","tid":1561330,"uid":273176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"我假設暫時連登風向都認同《願榮光歸香港》係國歌<br />\n咁麻煩各位香港人俾少少尊重<br />\n<br />\n「國歌演奏時常伴有具體的禮節要求，例如行軍禮、起立、脫帽等等，有些國家的領導人甚至在一些場合與到會人員齊唱，在一些國家還要求手撫胸口或鞠躬。在正式的外交場合這些禮節更為嚴格。」<br />\n<br />\n呢個係Wiki 嘅解釋，唔係話要跟足<br />\n但係國歌應該嚴肅少少，起碼收埋嬉皮笑臉<br />\n挺直條腰，尊重香港，向各義士致敬<br />\n<br />\n今日喺某商場一齊唱國歌 <br />\n一開頭都幾好，到9點11分仲一齊默哀<br />\n到後期開始膠化<br />\n<br />\n有人唱數碼暴龍  有人玩火車捐山窿<br />\n但另一邊就播國歌做背景音樂<br />\n之後唱國歌 啲人就走晒入中庭排排坐住唱 好似唱k 咁<br />\n<br />\n冇話嘉年華唔得 只係播緊唱緊嘅時候停一停<br />\n認真諗吓入獄 流血嘅義士 我諗冇人會笑得出<br />\n<br />\n要成為國歌 就要有佢獨特之處 <br />\n做到足 先分到我地唔要支那國歌 要一首屬於香港嘅國歌<br />\n如果唔係《願榮光歸香港》只會變做下一首今天我 一起舉傘<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post唔係想做「國歌法」<br />\n我希望大家可以從心去尊重國歌<br />\n而唔係要受一啲法則所限<br />\n冇理由識尊重美國國歌 唔識尊重自己國歌下話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c7af7f566dd35a4a2687037e7e9d3b0101b100","tid":1561330,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"eb1ffb1bde1879337a7bf999b8ffe9885dab8885","tid":1561330,"uid":273176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:26:51.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到 <br />\n麻煩認同嘅幫手推一推"},{"pid":"ce19538a38551b27656f9b95eb31adc8fbc37111","tid":1561330,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b7609df5a0771a44bd801d0312109fb173689f0","tid":1561330,"uid":743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97ddbfb171823595d20473cdeb78293a11c402e","tid":1561330,"uid":100371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4ad1b37dfc3d19d108d8f4618c64fcf84a24b16","tid":1561330,"uid":44874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f7c1cd55874bad750f891c9c70a538e95f9cfc","tid":1561330,"uid":743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"eb1ffb1bde1879337a7bf999b8ffe9885dab8885","tid":1561330,"uid":273176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:26:51.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到 <br />\n麻煩認同嘅幫手推一推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"都幾慘 咁長好難有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2ee1dbaf0471e3d77d4d2211876e61b7e97da7","tid":1561330,"uid":251154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0de728c5c1fce55e2dcf9d579c44d7ae9531305c","tid":1561330,"uid":35474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"同意 琴晚葵芳都係咁"},{"pid":"af4db89a6f2da764d7e4f301372df3d1d313a060","tid":1561