>\n<br />\n要成為國歌 就要有佢獨特之處 <br />\n做到足 先分到我地唔要支那國歌 要一首屬於香港嘅國歌<br />\n如果唔係《願榮光歸香港》只會變做下一首今天我 一起舉傘<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post唔係想做「國歌法」<br />\n我希望大家可以從心去尊重國歌<br />\n而唔係要受一啲法則所限<br />\n冇理由識尊重美國國歌 唔識尊重自己國歌下話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">運動膠化係衰亡嘅第一步<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2bc433646e2f651e3dacaf3fb6f27a63fd4b6a0c","tid":1561330,"uid":914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f86d7a99ea1cb1ad4d2d61d5f7aaa735ae38f60","tid":1561330,"uid":743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"好多嘢唔係得個講字<br />\n要做出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7401037bf0de32492c99ffd425e3e09491a29629","tid":1561330,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"係現場既表示<br />\n兩邊大堂分開左 現場好多聲音 其實聽唔到另一邊唱緊國歌 所以疊左<br />\n其實我地有嚴肅亦有輕鬆 大家多d互相配合互相理解啦 任何延續到運動既方法都應該做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75361fe502b67f72cd4392675b8d365a1e993a6b","tid":1561330,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c2c1286868f0b3218e1e88a97aece94e59389f","tid":1561330,"uid":168509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"或者搵人叫 肅立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n今日沙田有人叫 雖然周圍都笑左2聲 但見好多人都下意識企直左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n當然最好就自動自覺"},{"pid":"9769cb0b6b7b2fbd869f6ea73f835444809173d0","tid":1561330,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914109981a5d0ab3b9e8a80efc8ac9ada78c47b2","tid":1561330,"uid":259121,"like":0,"di